Quasar:



Quasar stood up and turned to Black Arachnia. She nodded in relpy to 
her orders. "Aye, miss." She transformed, pausing a moment on what 
happened. New form. She would have to get used to it. She was a 
hybrid sack sipider with teal and yellow coloring and a black head. 
Her legs were long and slender.

She turned and skittered into the hallway, down the many corridors.
